These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, french, canadian
There 3 different types of food: lime, mango, artichoke
3 different pets are kept: rat, mouse, horse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, may
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the nigerian is between the person eating mango and the person eating artichoke##2
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the french##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality         | french | nigerian   | canadian   |
| Food   | mango     | lime | artichoke |
| Pet   | horse  | rat    | mouse      |
| Birthday     | june     | april      | may |

