.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, reading
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, bongani
3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, canasta
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, teacher, architect
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing canasta##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person playing scrabble##1
5. the videographer is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's hobby is reading##2
6. the person who's hobby is reading is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Hobby          | fishing  | rock-climbing     | reading     |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | bongani     | dannemann      |
| Game   | canasta  | scrabble | chess |
| Job           | architect | videographer     | teacher       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, tulip
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, italian, dutch
3 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon, chess
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, september
1. the argentine is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the dutch and the person playing chess##2
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Flower          | dahlia  | tulip     | amaryllis     |
| Nationality           | dutch | argentine  | italian   |
| Game   | monopoly  | backgammon    | chess |
| Birthday           | september     | august | may |

