.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different games are played: chess, go, billiard
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance
City: london, rome, prague
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, russian
1. the colombian is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person playing billiard is between the person watching epic movies and the person traveling to london##2
4. the person playing go is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Game    | chess       | billiard  | go   |
| Movie-Genre     | epic    | romance  | disaster |
| City     | rome   | prague | london        |
| Nationality   | russian | colombian     | brazilian      |

