.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, sprite
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, tulip
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, apricot, white
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, siglo, montecristo
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is between the person who likes white and the person who growstulip##2
3. the person who growsbellflower is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage          | sprite    | cola     | almond-milk      |
| Flower         | bellflower | marigold | tulip |
| Color   | white  | apricot       | blue       |
| Cigar           | siglo     | fonseca       | montecristo     |

