There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, pink, coral
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the palace house is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who likes pink##2
4. the cottage house is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Sport          | cycling | swimming | badminton    |
| Cigar         | siglo | aristoff      | bolivar |
| House   | victorian   | palace     | cottage        |
