.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
City: prague, miami, hannover
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, baseball, handball
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, lemonade
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, poppy, dahlia
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who growszinnia##2
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is handball and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| City          | hannover      | miami   | prague |
| Sport         | climbing | baseball | handball |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | lemonade | tea   |
| Flower     | dahlia         | poppy  | zinnia       |

