.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, turquise, black
City: marseilles, boston, hamburg
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, asparagus
3 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, rat
1. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person eating plum is between the person traveling to boston and the person who likes black##2
5. the person who likes turquise is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Color      | blue       | turquise      | black      |
| City         | boston    | hamburg | marseilles      |
| Food           | asparagus | plum     | radish |
| Pet   | hamster     | rat          | turtle       |

