The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, chess, dancing
3 different games are played: go, domino, billiard
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, weightlifting, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person playing domino and the person playing billiard##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Flower      | lily      | tulip | dahlia     |
| Hobby          | chess   | traveling      | dancing     |
| Game   | billiard  | go      | domino |
| Sport     | surfing | soccer        | weightlifting     |

