.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, april, march
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, azalea, begonia
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, fanta
There 3 different types of food: pear, lemon, artichoke
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person drinking milk is the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person eating pear is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Birthday       | april       | march       | october    |
| Flower         | begonia | azalea | amaryllis |
| Beverage       | milk      | fanta         | hot-chocolate |
| Food   | pear        | artichoke            | lemon  |

