.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, april, january
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, epic, spy
There 3 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, nectarine
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, go
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person playing go##1
3. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
4. the person playing chess is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching action movies##2
5. the person eating nectarine is on the far left##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Birthday      | january     | april | march      |
| Movie-Genre         | epic  | spy       | action |
| Food   | nectarine   | artichoke         | apricot     |
| Game   | bridge | chess    | go     |

