House: craftsman, gothic-revival, colonial
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, game, alhambra
There 3 different types of food: garlic, mango, pear
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the colonial house##1
2. the game-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating pear##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the gothic-revival house and the game-smoker##2
6. the oliveros-smoker is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Sport      | cycling | snowboarding      | golf            |
| House           | craftsman | colonial | gothic-revival |
| Cigar   | game     | alhambra        | oliveros         |
| Food   | mango  | garlic    | pear        |

