.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, coffee
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, pink, blood-red
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, electrician, analyst
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, metal, classical
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the fan metal##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is between the fan techno and the person who likes grey##2
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the electrician is the fan techno##1
5. the analyst is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage       | coffee | almond-milk | 7up |
| Color         | grey   | blood-red       | pink        |
| Job       | analyst | paramedic   | electrician         |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | metal     | techno         |

