2. the art-deco house is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person eating garlic is the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking juice and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage           | water   | mirinda   | juice |
| Food   | garlic | raspberry   | cranberry     |
| Birthday   | december     | august      | march    |
| House           | gothic-revival | art-deco | farmhouse    |

