3. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the social-worker and the person who growszinnia##2
4. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is between the coach and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
