.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, baking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, april, october
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, fonseca, old-henry
City: colone, venice, rome
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person traveling to colone##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to colone##1
4. the game-smoker is the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person traveling to rome and the fonseca-smoker##2
6. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby        | skydiving      | magic-tricks | baking |
| Birthday         | april     | october    | july        |
| Cigar       | fonseca | old-henry   | game   |
| City   | colone          | venice     | rome       |

 